com.hazelcast.util.function

Interface Consumer<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the input to the operation
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClientEngine, InternalEventService, OperationExecutor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientEngineImpl, EventServiceImpl, InboundResponseHandler, InvocationMonitor, OperationExecutorImpl, PacketDispatcher, TcpIpConnectionManager

    public interface Consumer<T>
    Represents an operation that accepts a single input argument and returns no result. Unlike most other functional interfaces, Consumer is expected to operate via side-effects.
